{
  "id": "adv_main_03_11_03",
  "title": "BIG4編1章53話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんの迷いのなさの理由……ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason why DoriKyun doesn’t hesitate…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "れもんさんと来夢さんの背中を見て\nどりきゅんの強さの一端に触れることは出来た",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to get a glimpse of DoriKyun’s strength\nby watching Lemon-san and Laim-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……どうして、あの弱肉強食そのものみたいな\nスタンスなのかまでは分からなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…I wasn’t able to understand\nwhy they have that survival-of-the-fittest stance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それを知らない限り、私達がどりきゅんを超えることは\n出来ない気がするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like we won’t be able to surpass\nDoriKyun unless we know that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1775968075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "敵を知り、己を知れば、百戦危うからずと言いますしね\n理由や過程を知ることは、大事だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Know your enemy and know yourself‚ and you will not be imperiled in a hundred battles‚ they say.\nI think it’s important to know the reason and the process.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そのために、どりきゅんの過去……か。分かった\n俺も知らないから、まずは三枝さんに当たってみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So to do that…you want to know about DoriKyun’s past‚ huh. I understand.\nSince I don’t know either‚ I’ll ask Saegusa-san first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Manager-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3381183266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0251023571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 52.0251023452
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 52.2251023571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんの過去については\n三枝さんも詳しい情報は持っていないそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san said that he\ndoesn’t have any detailed information.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7601685976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんですね。三枝さんでも知らないなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is…that so? Even Saegusa-san doesn't know…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.942834723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "困りましたわね。誰に当たるといいのやら……あら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a problem. Who should we ask…? Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7333333294,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5433.333337299999,
          "startTime": 69.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様\nみんな揃って考え込んじゃって、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work.\nWhat’s the matter‚ everyone? Lost in thought like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 77.45871970000451,
          "startTime": 71.0340799811
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん。今、どりきゅんの過去を知ってる人が\nいないか探していたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ we’re looking for someone who might\nknow about DoriKyun's past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんのことか～……\nあの人達のことは私も知らないのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriKyun‚ huh~…\nI don’t really know much about them either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6192270441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "トーク番組にもほとんど出ないし\nインタビューも受けない……って業界で有名だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re famous in the industry for rarely appearing on talk shows‚\nand not doing interviews.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8525603774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "自分達の動画チャンネルでは沢山喋っていますが……\n確かに過去に言及することはありませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They talk a lot on their own video channels‚ though…\n…but you’re right‚ they never talk about their past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7858937107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……もしかしたらmihoさんなら\n何か知ってるんじゃないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ but…maybe Miho-san\nknows something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7192270441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 114.7948293327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんが一番活動歴が長いですからね\nそうか……星見プロのアイドルの中では",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miho-san has the longest career.\nRight…of the idols at Hoshimi Productions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7948293327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "大手の事務所に所属していたんだし\n業界の情報も入りやすいかもしれないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was part of a major agency‚\nso she might have easy access to information about the industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3871179743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんは、今収録中だから……\n終わり次第、俺の方から電話してみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miho-san is currently recording‚ so…\n…I’ll call her once she’s finished.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 134.6983893351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんの読みが当たってたみたいだ\nmihoさん、知っているような口ぶりだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like Haruko-san’s guess was right.\nMiho-san sounded like she knows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "やった！　予想的中！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did it! My prediction was right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1686320899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、仕事の用件じゃないなら連絡しないでって\n問答無用で電話を切られたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she told me not to contact her if it wasn’t for work‚\nand hung up on me without a word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3598463685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "その調子だと、簡単には教えてもらえそうにないですね\nmihoさんらしいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this rate‚ it doesn’t seem like she’ll tell us easily.\nThat's just like Miho-san‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……少なくとも、大勢で押しかけるのはやめた方が\n良さそうだ。騒がしいのは嫌がる人だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…At the very least‚ we should avoid showing up with a lot of people.\nShe dislikes it when it’s noisy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それなら――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ then――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.8615118063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん\n私が直接聞きに行ってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ Manager-san?\nMay I go ask her directly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 173.9360923723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
